{"id":644802,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/05/【cdtv】阿布鬧鬧：新疆街访后-来告诉你一些再教育/","date":"2020-05-19T01:26:11Z","modified":"2020-05-19T10:39:13Z","title":"【CDTV】阿布鬧鬧：新疆街访后 来告诉你一些再教育集中营的真相","content":"<p>5月19日，有推特网友转发一名台湾youtuber的新疆喀什vlog，该视频发布于2020年1月，这名颇有勇气的youtuber在一片老城废墟上通过镜头分享了自己对于新疆人权问题、集中营问题的看法，为维族人发声。</p>\n<p><iframe title=\"在新疆街訪後，來告訴你一些再教育集中營的真相\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/RJW3pSNGTAI?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">台灣知名Youtuber實地進入新疆喀什，親身談集中營，幾度哽咽分享感受，為維吾爾族人發聲。<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Xinjiang?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Xinjiang</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/CCP?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#CCP</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Uighurs?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Uighurs</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ConcentrationCamps?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ConcentrationCamps</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/RGZds96e2b\">pic.twitter.com/RGZds96e2b</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; EnlightenMedia (@enlightenmedia5) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/enlightenmedia5/status/1262476222379982848?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 18, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>从他的facebook社交动态看，这名youtuber在离境中国的时候受到了“百般刁难”与“搜查”，所幸拍摄的相关视频素材得以保留。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-644803\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020.1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"476\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020.1.png 928w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020.1-300x286.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020.1-768x732.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n","author":1002,"categories":[18271,38914,38927,38956],"tags":[38698,40593,36667,17915,12055,29378]}